# =============================================================================
# Docker 构建上下文忽略清单
# 作用:加快 docker build 上下文上传,并防止宿主机上平台相关的预编译产物
#       (尤其是 Windows 下编出的 backend/native/search-engine/index.node 与
#       target/)混入 Linux 镜像 —— Rust 插件必须在镜像内重新构建。
# =============================================================================

# --- 通用 ---
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.DS_Store
**/*.log
**/npm-debug.log*
**/.env
**/.env.local

# --- 依赖与产物(镜像内各自 npm ci / vite build / cargo build 重新生成)---
**/node_modules
backend/dist
backend/coverage
frontend/dist

# --- Rust 原生插件宿主机产物:严禁带入,镜像内必须重建 ---
backend/native/**/target
backend/native/**/index.node
backend/native/**/*.so
backend/native/**/*.dylib
backend/native/**/*.dll

# --- 其他 ---
**/.vscode
**/.idea
docs
*.md
